A family has been left in a state of shock and pain after their breadwinner, identified as “Iyke” was shot dead in front of his house in Choba, Rivers state by suspected cultists. The death of the man said to be a father of four has left community members in a state of fear. The cultists in Choba are gradually turning the town into a ghost town. Watch the video below: Father of four "iyke" shot dead in front of his house in Choba, Rivers state by unknow assailants. The cultists in Choba are gradually turning the town to a ghost town. Iyke was shot in the head. There are tens of other murders unreported. #saintavenueent A post shared by  Saint Avenue (@saintavenue_ent) on Aug 15, 2019 at 4:49am PDT Source